      <p></p>
<p>The loss of a friend leaves an irreplaceable gap.  These messages aim to offer solace and understanding to your friend during this profound sadness.</p>
<li>I am so incredibly sorry to hear about the loss of your dear friend.</li>
<li>My heart aches for you during this difficult time.</li>
<li> Thinking of you and sending my deepest condolences.</li>
<li> I'm here for you, whatever you need.  Don't hesitate to reach out.</li>
<li> Your friend will be dearly missed.</li>
<li> I will always remember (deceased's name)'s kindness and generosity.</li>
<li> Sending you strength and comfort.</li>
<li> I'm so sorry for your loss. Please know you are not alone.</li>
<li> May happy memories bring you comfort.</li>
<li> I'm thinking of you and sending love.</li>
<li> Your friend was a wonderful person, and they will be deeply missed.</li>
<li> I am here to listen if you want to talk.</li>
